data.name: label2.Text
data.value: This demo will test the details view mode for advanced functions like sorting, rating subitem support, images only, images and text view and finally the user draw mode. You need to take a look at the code to see how this work.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: This demo will test the the thumbnails view and drag and drop function. You should drag and drop IMAGES to this control. Use the bars below to adjust zooming and view. Please note that the drag and drop function works as same as in details view, changing view mode doesn't effect drag and drop.
